Class BioFeedbackService

java.lang.Object
  Service

SerialBTDevice.DeviceConnectionListener
public class BioFeedbackService
extends Service
implements SerialBTDevice.DeviceConnectionListener

Background service for use with AndroidSpineServer. Maintains list of Bluetooth devices which communicate with the main Spine server Provides communication between individual Bluetooth devices and the Spine Server.
